<h2>Web Component Usage</h2>
<p>Bolt Chip is a web component, you can simply use <code class="language-html">&lt;bolt-chip&gt;</code> in the markup to make it render.</p>
<h3>Example</h3>
<pre class="c-bolt-code-snippet-syntax--light"><code class="language-html">&lt;bolt-chip&gt;
  Text of the chip
&lt;/bolt-chip&gt;</code></pre>
<br>
<h3>Simple usage</h3>
<bolt-chip>
  Text of the chip
</bolt-chip>
<br><br>
<h3>Passing url</h3>
<bolt-chip url="!#">
  Chip with link
</bolt-chip>
